parameters:
Cerburus Octopus: Kekeke... I've prepared a surefire best-
selling product that'll skyrocket our sales! The right to
have unprotected sex with Shark Mountain Memimi, just for
250,000 yen a pop!!

Memimi: GYAAAAAAAHHH!!? What kind of thing are you trying to
sell?! Don't mess around!! Seriously!!

What awaited Memimi upon her return to the convenience store
was the announcement of a terrifying new product... For
200,000 yen, one could have the right to have unprotected
sex with a girl of idol-level supreme beauty. Naturally, it
wasn't clear who would be forced to have sex, making it the
worst product imaginable from the girls' perspective...

Cerburus Octopus: If you don't like it, you're free to quit
the convenience store and the organization. That is, if
you're okay with abandoning our great boss!! But I doubt
someone like Lord Shark Duke would do something like running
away after losing twice.

Memimi: ...Yeah, that's right, uh-huh... I definitely hate
the idea of being prostituted out to an unspecified number
of people... but having lost, I guess I'll go along with
it...

Memimi ended up having to sell the sex rights at the
convenience store...
